{{澳大利亞最大城市}}

=== 語言 ===
根据澳大利亚政府2016年的调查，在澳大利亚居住的人们在家中最普遍使用的語言，根据人数多少排序，依次是[[英語|英語]]（72.7%）、[[現代標準漢語|華語]]（2.5%）, [[阿拉伯語|阿拉伯語]]（1.4%），[[廣東話|廣東話]]（1.2%），[[越南語|越南語]]（1.2%）以及[[義大利語|義大利語]]（1.2%）<ref>{{Cite web|title=Main Features - Cultural Diversity Article|url=https://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/Lookup/by+Subject/2071.0~2016~Main+Features~Cultural+Diversity+Article~60|accessdate=2020-10-21|date=2017-06-28|last=Statistics|first=c=AU; o=Commonwealth of Australia; ou=Australian Bureau of|work=www.abs.gov.au|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405013012/https://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/Lookup/by+Subject/2071.0~2016~Main+Features~Cultural+Diversity+Article~60|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[英語|英語]]在從第一代英國移民到來後，就是澳洲最通用語言。原住民則部份保留著有使用母語者。<ref>{{cite book|url=http://www.rch.org.au/aedi/media/Snapshot_of_Early_Childhood_DevelopmentinAustralia_AEDI_National_Report.pdf |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110408162508/http://www.rch.org.au/aedi/media/Snapshot_of_Early_Childhood_DevelopmentinAustralia_AEDI_National_Report.pdf |archivedate=2011-04-08 |title=A Snapshot of Early Childhood Development in Australia| page= 8 |date=December 2009|isbn=978-0-9807246-0-8 |publisher=Australian Government Department of Education, Employment and Workplace Relations}}</ref><ref>[[Agence_France-Presse|Agence France-Presse]]/[[Jiji_Press|Jiji Press]], "Arabic Australia's second language", ''[[The_Japan_Times|The Japan Times]]'', 16 April 2011, p. 4.</ref>而許多第一第二代移民通常都是雙語人士。

[[澳大利亚原住民语言|澳大利亚原住民语言]]數量於歐洲殖民者初到澳洲時大概有250種語言，如今还剩20種原住民語言仍在各年齡層使用<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australiangeographic.com.au/news/2011/08/a-mission-to-save-indigenous-languages/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224075354/http://www.australiangeographic.com.au/news/2011/08/a-mission-to-save-indigenous-languages/ |archivedate=2013-12-24|title=A mission to save indigenous languages |publisher=Australian Geographic |accessdate=2016-03-18 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=nilsr/>，其中110種語言于年長者使用<ref name=nilsr>{{cite web |url=http://arts.gov.au/sites/default/files/pdfs/nils-report-2005.pdf |title=National Indigenous Languages Survey Report 2005 |publisher=Department of Communications, Information Technology and the Arts |accessdate=2009-09-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090709141342/http://www.arts.gov.au/indigenous/national_indigenous_languages_survey_report_2005 |archivedate=2009-07-09 |deadurl=yes  }}</ref>。根據2006年調查，52,000名澳洲原住民在家中使用原住民語言，約佔12%的原住民總人口<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/mf/4713.0 |title=4713.0 – Population Characteristics, Aboriginal and Torres Strait Islander Australians, 2006 |last=Australian Bureau of Statistics |date=2010-05-04 |publisher=Australian Bureau of Statistics |location=Canberra |accessdate=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2010-10-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101017150826/http://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/mf/4713.0 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。澳大利亞則有{{lang-en|澳大利亞手語|Auslan}}，為5,500名聽覺障礙人士的主要語言<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.censusdata.abs.gov.au/ABSNavigation/prenav/ViewData?action=404&documentproductno=0&documenttype=Details&order=1&tabname=Details&areacode=0&issue=2006&producttype=Census%20Tables&javascript=true&textversion=false&navmapdisplayed=true&breadcrumb=POTLD&&collection=Census&period=2006&productlabel=Language%20Spoken%20at%20Home%20(full%20classification%20list)%20by%20Sex&producttype=Census%20Tables&method=Place%20of%20Usual%20Residence&topic=Language& |title=20680-Language Spoken at Home (full classification list) by Sex – Australia |last=Australian Bureau of Statistics |date=2007-06-27 |work=2006 Census Tables : Australia |location=Canberra |publisher=Australian Bureau of Statistics |accessdate=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2013-07-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130723164830/http://www.censusdata.abs.gov.au/ABSNavigation/prenav/ViewData?action=404&documentproductno=0&documenttype=Details&order=1&tabname=Details&areacode=0&issue=2006&producttype=Census |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 宗教 ===
{{bar box
|title = 澳洲人口宗教信仰分佈<ref name="statcan1">{{cite web|url=https://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/Lookup/by%20Subject/2071.0~2016~Main%20Features~Religion%20Data%20Summary~70|title=Religion in Australia|publisher=Australian Bureau of Statistics|date=11 July 2018|access-date=26 August 2019|archive-date=2019-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190425101319/https://www.abs.gov.au/ausstats/abs@.nsf/Lookup/by|dead-url=no}}</ref>
|titlebar=#ddd |left1=宗教 |right1=百分比 |float=right
|bars =
{{bar percent|[[天主教|天主教]]|purple|22.6}}
{{bar percent|[[圣公宗|圣公宗]]|blue|13.3}}
{{bar percent|其他[[基督教|基督教]]|lightblue|16.3}}
{{bar percent|[[佛教|佛教]]|pink|2.4}}
{{bar percent|[[伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭教]]|green|2.6}}
{{bar percent|[[印度教|印度教]]|orange|1.9}}
{{bar percent|[[猶太教|猶太教]]|brown|0.4}}
{{bar percent|其他宗教|black|0.4}}
{{bar percent|[[無神論者|無神論者]]|red|30.1}}
{{bar percent|未定義及不確定|grey|9.7}}
